<br>
<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Pets can hold more than 8 items. Tukodo has the test right for that. Give pet a bag of summoned armour, 8 items. Give 2 lev rings (ac5 each), a summoned heatstone necklace (more ac), and a elemental defender (no idea if the pet puts it in the back slot or not). 12 items so far. Then give it 2 weapons, you will be able to see, or not be able to see the pet holding the 2 weapons. The pet holds them. So pets will hold the 13th and 14th items you give to them.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
