When a melee procs a weapon, you don't see them casting a spell. I group with some of the highest end people on my server, as I am in the second best guild on my server. About half of them have weapons that proc in some way, be it Avatar, or Flame of the Efreeti, or Combust, or Careless Lightning.  I have -all- my spell information on in a little window to the side, so that I know who is casting what and when. Whenever they proc, you just see the message, except for a ranger using that fire proc buff, because that proc actually has a cast time and can be interrupted.<br>
