<br>
I was 24th (or maybe 20th) level when Luclin was released and the summoned phatom armor and focus items became available.  I was fighting craig spiders in East Karana.  It was all I could do to keep the water pet alive {I made sure I had either the best pet before tackling the craig spiders} before the craig spider died.  Occasionlly, the pet died.  <br>
<br>
I first tested just the summoned phatom armor.  I fought 10 craig spiders and not once did the pet come close to dying.  It often had slightly more that full blub of health left.  Then I summoned and tested a new pet and gave it the focus items.  I again fought 10 craig spiders, and not once did the pet die.  However, it had slightly less that one bulb of heath left.  I then gave the pet armor too and tested 10 more craig spiders.  The pet ended up with about 1.5 blubs of health left.  That was giving the pet 7 pieces of armor plus 5 focus items plus two weapons and the elemental defender.  <br>
<br>
This testing was done over a year ago so things may have changed, but I still don't believe there is an 8 piece limit on items the pet can use.  <br>
<br>
After you have camped the same mobs for awhile, you can tell when you forgot to give the pet armor or gave it to them in a bag, or forgot to give it the focus items.<br>
<br>
I still don't believe there is an 8 piece limit on items the pet can use.   <p></p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top">  Page <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showMessageRange?topicID=918.topic&start=1&stop=20>1</a><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showMessageRange?topicID=918.topic&start=21&stop=40>2</a> <b>3</b> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showMessageRange?topicID=918.topic&start=61&stop=74>4</a> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showPrevMessage?topicID=918.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showNextMessage?topicID=918.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=918.topic&index=60><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/addReply.gif border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"><a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.threadControl?topicID=918.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/softsky/unread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=918.topic>Subscribe</a> Click to receive email notification of replies<br>  <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerfrm29.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=918.topic>Unsubscribe</a> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies<br> </td><td align="right" valign="top"></td></tr><tr align="right"><td colspan=2><form action=http://pub102.ezboard.com/BBSForum.jumpShowForum method=post><table border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="1"><tr><td><b>jump to:</b><select name=forumName><option value="themagicianstowerannouncem